iTo use the filtering feature, you can either:		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- Point the IP of comment.bilibili.com to 127.0.0.1 via the hosts		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ifile, or		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- Use browser extensions like FoxyProxy or SwitchyOmega to route		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
icomment.bilibili.com traffic through the program's proxy port.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
