iThe program's features include:		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iTop/Bottom Danmaku Filtering		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- : Only retains "Science Populizers" (users posting multiple		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
itop/bottom danmaku in a short time) and "Subtitle Providers" (users		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iposting multiple top/bottom danmaku throughout the video). All others		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iare reset to scrolling danmaku.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iIntelligent Keyword Filtering		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- : For certain keywords (e.g., "Jinkela"), they are only allowed when		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iappearing frequently in danmaku, avoiding interference with videos		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
irelated to these keywords.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iRepetitive Text Truncation		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- : For danmaku with consecutive repeated characters (e.g., "23333",		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i"66666", "hhhhh"), reduces repetitions to a maximum of 5 characters.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iDanmaku Density Control		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- : When the screen floods with identical danmaku, reduces the		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iquantity to the square root of the original count.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iFont Size Reset		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- : Default scrolling danmaku are set to a small font size.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
